@ProductCatalog_HostAddress = http://localhost:5053

### Product Catalog API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@apiGatewayUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get All Products (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get Products by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10&category=Electronics

### Search Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search?query=laptop

### Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/67123abc456def789012345

### Create Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dell XPS 15 Laptop",
  "description": "High-performance laptop with Intel i7 processor, 16GB RAM, and 512GB SSD",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/dell-xps-15.jpg",
  "stockQuantity": 25,
  "tags": ["laptop", "dell", "electronics", "computer"]
}

### Create Another Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse",
  "description": "Ergonomic wireless mouse with adjustable DPI",
  "price": 29.99,
  "category": "Accessories",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/wireless-mouse.jpg",
  "stockQuantity": 100,
  "tags": ["mouse", "wireless", "accessories"]
}

### Update Product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/67123abc456def789012345
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dell XPS 15 Laptop - Updated",
  "price": 1199.99,
  "stockQuantity": 30,
  "isAvailable": true
}

### Update Product Stock
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/67123abc456def789012345/stock
Content-Type: application/json

-5

### Delete Product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/67123abc456def789012345

### Via API Gateway - Get All Products
GET {{apiGatewayUrl}}/products?page=1&pageSize=10

### Via API Gateway - Create Product
POST {{apiGatewayUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

